        "content": "### Pipeline Quick Actions\n- Control channel: `docker logs internet-monitoring-pipeline-server-1 --since 5m`\n- Replay sensor queue: `docker exec -it internet-monitoring-pipeline-agent-1 sqlite3 /var/lib/pipeline/queue.db \"SELECT * FROM chunks\"`\n- Snapshot stream: `wscat -H \"Authorization: Bearer <stream-token>\" ws://<cloud-ip>:8766`\n- Manual send: see README section 6.4\n\nTokens & TLS live in group vars; rerun Ansible after updates."
